This Map is used to combine the registration information of this batch. 
In this improvement, LRU can be access across batches. It is used to cache the registration information to reduce access to data sources.

I also encountered the same problem. After testing, I found that some oap servers find elasticSearch when they write data and there is an exception, which can cause stop writing elasticSearch. If the agent selects this oap server to report data, it will cause the above problemï¼ŒThe problem can be resolved temporarily by restarting the oap server, but the following issues need to be resolved in the end
1. Agent is highly available. When reporting data to the bottleneck, select other nodes or multiple nodes to report, rather than fixing one oap server node;
2. Oap server needs to add write exception retry;

